This contemporary bed combines a bed, a bookcase and a storage area all in one charming piece. Solid pine construction with a honey-colored finish gives this bookcase bed a rustic country feel. The bed's shelf area and drawers provide plenty of space for storing your child's books, clothes and toys.
Accommodates 8-inch mattress
